Title: Noncommutative gerbes and deformation quantization
Authors: Paolo Aschieri, Igor Bakovic, Branislav Jurco, Peter Schupp
Comments: 10 pages
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Quantum Algebra; Symplectic Geometry
\\
  We define noncommutative gerbes using the language of star products.
Quantized twisted Poisson structures are discussed as an explicit realization
in the sense of deformation quantization. Our motivation is the noncommutative
description of D-branes in the presence of topologically non-trivial background
fields.
